"{\"uid\": \"ukrinform.net-rubric-sports-3891971-ukrainian-boxer-khyzhniak-wins-through-to-2024-olympics-final.html\", \"text\": \"Saturday, 21 March 2026, 14:47  21 March 2026  According to Ukrinform, the 28-year-old Ukrainian defeated two-time Olympic champion Arlen Lopez of Cuba in the semi-finals.  In the final match on August 7, Khyzhniak will face Nurbek Oralbay of Kazakhstan.  Photo: Getty Images  Topics  Agency  While citing and using any materials on the Internet, links to the website ukrinform.net not lower than the first paragraph are mandatory. In addition, citing the translated materials of foreign media outlets is possible only if there is a link to the website ukrinform.net and the website of a foreign media outlet. Materials marked as \\\"Advertisement\\\" or with a disclaimer reading \\\"The material has been posted in accordance with Part 3 of Article 9 of the Law of Ukraine \\\"On Advertising\\\" No. 270/96-VR of July 3, 1996 and the Law of Ukraine \\\"On the Media\\\" No. 2849-\\u0425 of March 31, 2023 and on the basis of an agreement/invoice.  Online media entity; Media identifier - R40-01421.  \\u00a9 2015-2026 Ukrinform. All rights reserved.  \"}"